<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٦) وَمَزْبَلَةٍ <span class="c2">(٢)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٧) وَقَارِعَةِ طَرِيقٍ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٨) وَلَا فِي <span class="c2">(٣)</span> أَسْطِحَتِهَا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[٥]</span> الخَامِسُ: اسْتِقْبَالُ القِبْلَةِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>- وَلَا تَصِحُّ بِدُونِهِ،<span class="c5"> إِلَّا:</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>- لِعَاجِزٍ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>- وَمُتَنَفِّلٍ فِي سَفَرٍ مُبَاحٍ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَفرْضُ قَرِيبٍ مِنْهَا:</span> إِصَابَةُ عَيْنِهَا.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَبَعِيدٍ:</span> جِهَتُهَا.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَيَعْمَلُ وُجُوباً:</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>- بِخَبَرِ ثِقَةٍ بِيَقِينٍ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>- وَبِمَحَارِيبِ المُسْلِمِينَ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَإِنِ اشْتَبَهَتْ فِي السَّفَرِ:</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) المجزرة: المكان الذي تجزر فيه المواشي. ينظر: المطلع ص ٨٤.<br>(٢) المزبلة: موضع الزبل، بفتح الباء وضمها. ينظر: المطلع ص ٨٤.<br>(٣) في (ب): على.</p> </div>